lemma rel_generatD': "rel_generat A Out R x y \<Longrightarrow> (is_Pure x \<longleftrightarrow> is_Pure y) \<and> (is_Pure x \<longrightarrow> is_Pure y \<longrightarrow> A (result x) (result y)) \<and> (\<not> is_Pure x \<longrightarrow> \<not> is_Pure y \<longrightarrow> Out (output x) (output y) \<and> R (continuation x) (continuation y))"
